<div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
  <img class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/62/Ruby_On_Rails_Logo.svg/1200px-Ruby_On_Rails_Logo.svg.png" alt="" width="600" height="300">
  <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Ruby on Rails Challenge</h1>
  <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
    <p class="lead mb-4">
      * You can search for any user by its name in the navbar
    </p>
    <p class="lead mb-4">
      * If you was't run the `rails db:seed` feel free to click in the button below and create all the users using the
      <%= link_to "Random User - API", "https://randomuser.me/api", target: :_blank %>
    </p>
    <p class="lead mb-4">
      * Feel free to contat me in any social media and tell me about what do you think about this project? What can I improve?
    </p>

    <p class="lead mb-4">
      I hope you enjoy!
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="50" height="50" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-emoji-smile" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
        <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
        <path d="M4.285 9.567a.5.5 0 0 1 .683.183A3.498 3.498 0 0 0 8 11.5a3.498 3.498 0 0 0 3.032-1.75.5.5 0 1 1 .866.5A4.498 4.498 0 0 1 8 12.5a4.498 4.498 0 0 1-3.898-2.25.5.5 0 0 1 .183-.683zM7 6.5C7 7.328 6.552 8 6 8s-1-.672-1-1.5S5.448 5 6 5s1 .672 1 1.5zm4 0c0 .828-.448 1.5-1 1.5s-1-.672-1-1.5S9.448 5 10 5s1 .672 1 1.5z"/>
      </svg>
    </p>
    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
      <%= link_to "Create Users List", create_users_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4 gap-3" %>
      <%= link_to "View Users", users_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
